sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as App Component
    participant Service as WeatherService
    participant Factory as WeatherFactory

    User->>UI: Click "Update Weather"
    UI->>Service: updateWeather()
    activate Service
    
    Service->>Factory: createRandomCondition()
    activate Factory
    Factory-->>Service: return new Condition (e.g. Sunny)
    deactivate Factory

    Service->>Service: new WeatherData(temp, condition)
    Service-->>UI: return WeatherData
    deactivate Service

    UI->>User: Update View (Re-render)